data.description: Great brick ranch ready to see a new owner within the Westland Sub known for its convenient proximity to local amenities, schools, and parks. Midcentury modern 3 bedroom 1.5 bath ready for your creative touch with hardwood floors throughout the main floor.  The fully finished basement provides lots of additional living space with a large rec room, wet bar, fireplace, half bath and numerous storage closets. Other great features including the nice size fenced in-yard and 2 car garage.
